Quickstrike:




Quickstrike squinted at Dark Mouse, letting a grin appear on his 
mouth-plate. "Ah don't mind." He watched a few seconds as she worked, 
wanting to help her in some way, despite his physical flaws. But he didn't 
know what good he would do. He may just get in the way.

Something hard hit the top of his head, freezing his thoughts. He cried out 
in pain, grabbing for his head. He looked down, seeing that a heavy shard of 
rock had broken off from the ceiling of the tunnel. That was the signal for 
him to get the Inferno out of there. He wasn't needed.

He ducked his head, a little embarassed. "Ah'll jus' go. Hollar if ya need 
anythin'!" He walked out as quickly as he could. As he exited, he saw that 
his body was covered in black dust and soot. He wiped at his arms and chest. 
He would have to clean this off. He transformed to beast mode and left the 
cave.
